<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 13:09:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>麻省理工学院哥德尔·埃舍尔·巴赫讲座</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mit-godel-escher-bach-lecture</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 13:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mit-godel-escher-bach-lecture</guid></item><item><title>确定驱动严重病毒感染的细胞蛋白</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/cell-proteins-that-drive-severe-viral-infections-identified</link><description>在最近发表的两项研究中，核孔蛋白 NUP98 和 NUP153 已被确定为正黄病毒感染的关键宿主因子。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/cell-proteins-that-drive-severe-viral-infections-identified2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 12:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/cell-proteins-that-drive-severe-viral-infections-identified</guid></item><item><title>AI 驱动的实验室在 12 小时内发现了更亮的无铅纳米材料</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/ai-powered-lab-discovers-brighter-lead-free-nanomaterials-in-12-hours</link><description>一个新的自主实验室最近在短短 12 小时内浏览了数十亿种潜在的材料合成配方，识别出了更亮的无铅发光​​纳米材料。这项工作可以加速更安全的发光纳米片的开发，其应用范围从光电探测器到太阳能燃料生产。描述这项工作的论文&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-powered-lab-discovers-brighter-lead-free-nanomaterials-in-12-hours.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 12:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/ai-powered-lab-discovers-brighter-lead-free-nanomaterials-in-12-hours</guid></item><item><title>引力常数的值仍然悬而未决</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/gravitational-constants-value-still-up-in-the-air</link><description>研究人员重复了对基本常数 G 的关键测量，但结果仍然不一致，凸显了将重力置于众所周知的尺度上的困难。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gravitational-constants-value-still-up-in-the-air.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 12:24:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/gravitational-constants-value-still-up-in-the-air</guid></item><item><title>量子纠错面临另一个障碍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/quantum-error-correction-faces-another-hurdle</link><description>新发现的超导量子位中的相关错误可能会限制实用量子计算机所需的纠错方案的性能。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/quantum-error-correction-faces-another-hurdle.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 12:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/quantum-error-correction-faces-another-hurdle</guid></item><item><title>光学暗伽马射线爆发揭示了异常宽的射流</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/optically-dark-gamma-ray-burst-reveals-an-unusually-wide-jet</link><description>一个国际天文学家小组使用各种望远镜对最近发现的伽马射线爆发源（GRB 250416C）进行了多波长观测。观察活动的结果， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/optically-dark-gamma-ray-burst-reveals-an-unusually-wide-jet2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 11:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/optically-dark-gamma-ray-burst-reveals-an-unusually-wide-jet</guid></item><item><title>超越国界：Metaverse 制造设想基于数字孪生的人工智能本地生产</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/beyond-borders-metaverse-manufacturing-envisions-ai-linked-local-production-built-on-digital-twins</link><description>过去几十年来，技术进步推动了广泛领域的巨大创新。人工智能 (AI) 系统、三维 (3D) 和四维 (4D) 打印、数字孪生（即物理对象、系统或流程的虚拟表示）和先进机器人等新兴和快速发展的技术将进一步改变许多行业和部门。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/beyond-borders-metaverse-manufacturing-envisions-ai-linked-local-production-built-on-digital-twins.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 11:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/beyond-borders-metaverse-manufacturing-envisions-ai-linked-local-production-built-on-digital-twins</guid></item><item><title>经过40年的等待，技术终于实现了三边拉链设计</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/after-a-40-year-wait-technology-finally-enables-three-sided-zipper-design</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 11:24:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/after-a-40-year-wait-technology-finally-enables-three-sided-zipper-design</guid></item><item><title>DNA 读取 AI 在几分钟内重建祖先，匹配顶级统计方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/dna-reading-ai-reconstructs-ancestry-in-minutes-matching-top-statistical-methods</link><description>俄勒冈大学的研究人员开发了一种人工智能工具，可以像 ChatGPT 等大型语言模型读取文本一样读取遗传密码。计算机模型扫描基因组中的生物突变模式，将成对的基因追溯到它们最后的共同祖先。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/dna-reading-ai-reconstructs-ancestry-in-minutes-matching-top-statistical-methods2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 11:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/dna-reading-ai-reconstructs-ancestry-in-minutes-matching-top-statistical-methods</guid></item><item><title>同步加速器 X 射线发现隐藏的蛋白质结合位点，实现两项新功能</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/synchrotron-x-rays-uncover-hidden-protein-binding-sites-enabling-two-new-functions</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 May 2026 10:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/synchrotron-x-rays-uncover-hidden-protein-binding-sites-enabling-two-new-functions</guid></item></channel></rss>